StringValues.15: The translation of a message carried by powerful Shadows.

Pages.Text:
We all one
One voice
One form
Praise
One
Beyond
Nameless
Eternal
All

Latecomer
Thieves
Bicker
Foolish

Herald
Seeks pain

Circle
Seeks power

Our body:
Shares not
These aims

Our body:
Carry tokens
Spread vision
All that serve
One
Not created
Or swayed
By latecomers

Our body:
Ready
Possible need
Act 
Should Herald
Its circle
Neglect
One

Our body:
Loose Primes
Not-us-servants
Summon Breath
That turns
Loose opener
Of ways
Break bindings
Unravel web

Our body:
Sundering repaired
One
Quickened
Accomplish
Beginning-all-time
All-one-together
Change-constant
As once was
So shall be
Forever
